<https://w3id.org/cq2onto/benchmark/ALL> a ftr:Benchmark ;
    dcterms:title "OntologyEngineeringEvaluationBenchmark"@en ;
    dcterms:description "Comprehensive evaluation framework for assessing how well large language models (LLMs) can generate and match ontology concepts, properties, axioms, and competency-question answers against gold-standard ontology definitions."@en .
